dc_title_s: Middlesex County, New Jersey 1850 wall map
dc_description_s: Map of Middlesex County, New Jersey entirely from original surveys. Color coded by township or borough and all property or home owners are listed. Insets of Perth Amboy and New Brunswick. Statistical table of acreage and square miles of each township and population of North Brunswick. Legend indicates churches, mills, post office and other buildings.|Fraying around edges.
